organic.title: NSE to launch derivatives on Nifty Next 50 index from April ...
organic.description: NSE to launch derivatives on Nifty Next 50 index from April 24. The exchange will offer three serial monthly index futures and index options contract cycles.

organic.description: NSE will be introducing Futures and Options contracts on Nifty Next 50 Index wef April 24, 2024. The Nifty Next 50 Index represents 50 companies from Nifty 100.

organic.title: Nifty 50 drops 200 points in two minutes, recovers 160 ...
organic.description: Nifty 50 index witnessed a sharp volatility as it dipped around 200 points in two minutes and then recovered by 160 points in the next seven minutes.

organic.title: 'Astonishing' spike in Nifty 50 put option, premium shoots ...
organic.description: The premium of Nifty 50 Put 22300 went from Rs 39.65 to Rs 250 in a minute candle and then shot up to Rs 392.25, pointed out trader Santosh Kumar Pasi.

organic.title: NSE Introduces Derivatives on Nifty Next 50 Index
organic.description: NSE has secured approval from SEBI for introducing Derivatives on the Nifty Next 50 index (NIFTYNXT50). Scheduled for launch on April 24, 2024.

organic.title: What Is Nifty FMCG? - Meaning, Advantages & How to Invest
organic.description: Nifty FMCG is a stock market index under the National Stock Exchange (NSE) of India, specifically representing the Fast Moving Consumer Goods (FMCG) sector.

organic.title: F&O trading on Nifty Next 50 index to start from next week
organic.description: SEBI gave its nod for trading in the futures and options (F&O) contracts on the Nifty Next 50 index which will start from Wednesday, April 24.
